00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:07,400
Ja...

209
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:09,400
Wat deden we daar nog meer?

210
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,400
In de zomer gingen we met vakantie.

211
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:13,400
Ja, in de zomer.

212
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:15,400
Ja, inderdaad.

213
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:17,400
Wanneer het in Nederland zomer is...

214
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:19,400
Dan is het daar in Indonesië...

215
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:21,400
Extra warm.

216
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:23,400
Dus dat noemen ze ook maar zomer.

217
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:25,400
Dus dan gingen we naar de bergen toe.

218
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:27,400
Kijk...

219
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:29,400
Nou, de naam ben ik even vergeten.

220
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:31,400
Later is het een...

